Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:50.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make waves, jump from your sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:50.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,arienai sekai wo iku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:55.23,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the unbelievable world
