Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:02.66,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Being brazen, is it a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:02.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shimeitehai->tsumari Winner (･∀･)
