Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:19.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost, One Piece, I’ll be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:19.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume miru kokoro wa choo dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:23.64,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreaming heart is huge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:23.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,samenai koto ga daiji--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:27.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s important not to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.91,0:01:27.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
