Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:48.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:48.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:53.67,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.69,0:01:53.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.69,0:01:56.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:01:56.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:02:00.34,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.36,0:02:00.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.36,0:02:04.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m aiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:04.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:07.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:07.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:11.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:11.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:15.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:15.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:19.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:19.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:27.71,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:28.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:35.25,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.27,0:02:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are after the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.15,0:02:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:03:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber\N after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally \Nentered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the harshest sea ruled\N by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After receiving an emergency signal,\N they landed on Punk Hazard Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a strange island \Ndivided into two parts;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Burning Lands and the Ice Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's the Straw Hats or Smoker,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can get rid of all those troublemakers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who are learning what's \Ngoing on on this island at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never understood why you joined\N the Warlords in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:04:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things that you can't see
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless you change your standing, Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scalpel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to tell you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:56.11,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Meeting Again After Two Years!\NLuffy and Law!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tashigi-chan!\NHe's way too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.15,0:05:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't join the Navy \Nto cower behind rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will get chopped up again in that film!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it up to Smo-yan for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? The film is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Alliga-taur!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.55,0:05:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a warship?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the Navy's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I didn't see anything \Naround here little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?\NIs the Master okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, somebody is there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you! Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your help the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat-ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the guy we met at the\NHuman Shoppe in Sabaody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Trafalgar Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's Traf... Tra-guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's his name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He helped me get away from the battlefield
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and treated my wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Jimbei, he saved my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:07:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect to see you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for helping me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the talking bear and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put Straw Hat-ya on my ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna help him get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take care of him for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going to happen \Nif we leave him like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said when we got here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if his wound opens up, he will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat-ya must take a \Ncomplete rest for two more weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you made it, Straw Hat-ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't have to thank me for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just did it on the spur of the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:08:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are both pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all enemies when it comes\N to the fight for the One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.39,0:08:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I owe so many people for\N helping me two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just saw Jimbei and now you - I'm so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there is a Navy soldier on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, help me, Trafalgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smo-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, Luffy!\NThe Navy's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain-chan, what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You alright, Smo-yan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker-san!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so! It's Smokey and his clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a hole in his chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:27.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To become a member of the Warlords...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:30.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,...he delivered the hearts \Nof one hundred pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:31.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,to the headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:39.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,He's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa whoa, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:10:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like these lame\N tearjerking scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! He took her down again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smo-san's on the ground, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he just do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She never learns.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Let's go!\NIt's dangerous here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tra-guy, I wanna ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go round to the back of the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you're looking for is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see each other again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We both have something we want to take back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. He was talking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't be here.\NI'm a former pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Luffy, let's get away from the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Smokey and his clan will be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they lose to Tra-guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! This is no time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smo-san and Captain-chan are injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:55.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:56.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}A MOUNTAIN BEHIND THE LABORATORY\NSANJI'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:59.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's remove this fur and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think we can find \Nany warm coats around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there a lodge or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need a camera and a mirror - \Nand a sh-shower would be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up or I'll tie you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's who?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The robot is scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's come to this, you people,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to put a leaf on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.66,0:12:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids are collapsing from cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't see any plants on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there are no leaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then a stone or whatever is fine! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get them for the kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got it. Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a spell-to-make-it-not-cold\N kind of bullshit, I'll kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.99,0:13:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poof!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a coat and boots!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! How did you do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gloves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is I ate an unusual fruit one day
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and since then, I can use magic \Nwhich allows me to disguise myself
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or everyone else in any way I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about foreign \Nclothes but will these suffice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:13:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.24,0:14:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's magic, if you take those\N clothes off, they'll disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool! Head man! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shouldn't have done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's a Devil Fruit eater?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had such power,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why didn't you do it sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It was nice to see her in a breast-band.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't wanna cover it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It itches! Itchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never say "ouch" or "I'm cold," will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are! Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Usopp! Robin! Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that jackass cook jumping around?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went nuts from cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? They look like giant children to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:02.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}THE STRAW HATS' ENCAMPMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here! This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:08.35,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,This building has a similar style as the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's crumbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like there was a \Nhuge explosion or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine as long as it'll \Nshelter us from the blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, where should we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hurt my own delicate body!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sanji-kun!\NWhat are you doing to my body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got my legs back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leg-maro! Oh my hind legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.96,0:16:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you there is no creature like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:17:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How surreal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's quite original.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The skeleton...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Just talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Nami-Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream of crossing a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a river running\N through giant boobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do the tank thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show us the laser beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it in his body?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to smoke, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk like adults, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Now, who is who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come to me when you get wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never shoot the laser beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is our...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I always that indecent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hurt Nami-san anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you touch my body, \NI'll make you pay 200,000 berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peeping will be 100,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.23,0:18:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't be so funny if it happened to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get it straight from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the samurai from the Wano Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:19:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The signal that we received was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...meant for the Alliga-taur
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who they call "Boss" from one of his men.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all started when this samurai\N sliced up all those centaurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I just wanted to rescue my missing \Nson - Momonosuke and cut those people
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because they were standing in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.81,0:19:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That many children were \Nheld captive in the facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Momonosuke is still there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, there were more children.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even know the \Nnewcomers that well yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the question is what \Nhappened after the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that man we just saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People were saying that he is a Warlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Tra-guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he become a Warlord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he joined them within past two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.27,0:20:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He chopped me up into three\N pieces before I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My head was kept in the facility!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My torso was left there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my legs were chased by a beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.49,0:20:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When my legs were trying to \Nget away using their wits,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they stuck onto something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was the back of the dragon's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, you were cursing about a Warlord!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? There were just legs, weren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did he speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my farts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has always been my specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were fart-talking?! Yuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it smells when we're in a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How funny to see a person \Nwith just a head and legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By contrast, I just saw \Nsomeone with just a torso.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.83,0:21:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was his torso, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.08,0:21:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.21,0:21:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you see my torso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Are you... Tashigi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! So you're really Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got switched?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!\NHow did this happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, are you okay without\N a heart, Tashigi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to talk to Captain-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one is so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.96,0:21:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smo-yan with Tashigi-chan's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It says "CC" on a ship hidden\N beside the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:22:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? There was such a ship,\NVice Admiral Smoker?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.52,0:22:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If it's left over from old days,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.23,0:22:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the mark should be "PH"...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.52,0:22:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...standing for Punk Hazard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.65,0:22:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is some mastermind behind Law
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.82,0:22:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and if "CC" are his initials,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.28,0:22:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I know who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's here on this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.71,0:22:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it makes a lot of senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.39,0:22:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the former colleague of Dr.Vegapunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.06,0:22:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a scientist
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.60,0:22:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,named Caesar Clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.11,0:22:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell have you done, Law?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.87,0:23:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who should be complaining here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.58,0:23:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.33,0:23:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the tumultuous New World, the ruler of Punk Hazard...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...turns out to be an unexpectedly well-respected figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.47,0:23:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the Straw Hats recoil from this shocking fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.35,0:23:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Smoker tries to discover the true identity of this mysterious master.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.64,0:23:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Worst in the World!\NA Scientist of Terror - Caesar!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
